-- Sirius reaches 6 mln subscribers, free cash flow positive
-- 
-- Tue Jan 2, 2007 4:07pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/02/businesspro-sirius-subscribers-dc-idUSWEN167020070102

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Sirius Satellite Radio Inc. ( SIRI.O ) 
said on Tuesday it ended 2006 with 6.024 million subscribers 
and achieved its first quarter of positive free cash flow in 
the fourth quarter in line with its expectations. 

  Sirius had said in early December that it expected to end 
the year with between 5.9 million and 6.1 million customers and 
that after capital spending it could report free cash flow for 
the quarter.